				Change Log
1.4	2018-9-2
	* It works faster because the result of each language will be printed
	as it is calculated

1.3	2018-1-1
	* Added support for Python

1.2	2018-1-1
	* Added support for HTML/CSS/JavaScript

1.1-r1	2017-12-27
	* Added support for C headers

1.1	2017-12-26
	* The program will no longer be copied to every project's root folder
	* You can now type `lines .' to calculate the lines of code in this directory
	* This program will check if the directory exists and will use current directory if no arguments given

1.0	2017-12-26
	* Initial Update of this project
